# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Environment configuration — copy this file to .env.local for local dev, and
# set the same VITE_* vars in your host (e.g. Vercel → Settings → Environment
# Variables) for production. .env.local is gitignored; never commit real keys.
#
# Each company/tenant gets its OWN Supabase project — fill these with THAT
# project's values (Supabase Dashboard → Project Settings → API).
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Frontend (Vite) — exposed in the browser bundle. The anon key is safe to ship
# publicly because Row-Level Security protects the data (see supabase/migrations).
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-ref.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Edge Function secrets — these are NOT used by the frontend. Set them on the
# Supabase project instead of here, with:
#   supabase secrets set ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=... PDL_API_KEY=...
# (SUPABASE_URL, SUPABASE_ANON_KEY, and SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY are injected
# into functions automatically by Supabase — you do not set them.)
#
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY   # AI features (ai-query, generate/score-assessment, coaching)
# PDL_API_KEY         # People Data Labs — candidate sourcing (source-candidates)
#
# Company identity used in candidate/new-hire-facing AI copy + emails. If unset,
# these fall back to QumulusAI defaults — set them per tenant when rebranding:
#   supabase secrets set COMPANY_NAME="Acme Corp" \
#     COMPANY_CONTEXT="a fintech company building payments infrastructure, based in Austin, TX" \
#     APP_URL="https://acme-hr.vercel.app"
#
# COMPANY_NAME        # e.g. "Acme Corp"  — appears in assessment/welcome emails & AI prompts
# COMPANY_CONTEXT     # one-line description of the company for AI scoring/onboarding context
# APP_URL             # deployed app URL used in new-hire login emails
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
